*splashutils-0.9_rc1 (12 Nov 2004)

  12 Nov 2004; Michal Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org>
  +splashutils-0.9_rc1.ebuild:
  A new bugfix release. Closes #68853 and #70029. Fixes some theme issues
